{"tid":2447150,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"北京拒為長期病長者打疫苗","createTime":"2021-03-15T04:12:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T05:14:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1441910b5cf4f1ecf0f6fd80e3dbe6e19faa5466","tid":2447150,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T04:12:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210315/TRYCI6SYMFHH5GFWPJMSNZPK4A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210315%2FTRYCI6SYMFHH5GFWPJMSNZPK4A%2F&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDoVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=808f194c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210315%2FTRYCI6SYMFHH5GFWPJMSNZPK4A%2F&h=e9092a94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210315/TRYCI6SYMFHH5GFWPJMSNZPK4A/</a><br />\n<br />\n北京拒為長期病長者打疫苗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/4vUb0AY-0Wu7XsvA544Ekf4EwBs=/1000x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YNNRC4KEE5CN7NUMAZ45KOKF7E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F4vUb0AY-0Wu7XsvA544Ekf4EwBs%3D%2F1000x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYNNRC4KEE5CN7NUMAZ45KOKF7E.jpg&h=4d595028&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■北京有疫苗接種點設長者專用通道。<br />\n<br />\n國家衞健委早前曾表示，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n內媒報道，北京朝陽。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n有長者被安排到接種點的緊急醫療區，接受數次血壓測量不合格後，被拒接種疫苗。有接種點負責人解釋，慢性病的急性發作期或嚴重慢性疾病患者均不適合接種疫苗，患有惡性腫瘤者也暫不予接種。<br />\n<br />\n內地之前未禁止長者接種疫苗，但是在接種同意書中，明確標示「60歲以上人群」不屬於接種範圍。本港則未有相關指引，甚至將長者列為優先接種組別。早前接種科興疫苗後死亡的六名港人中，至少四人有糖尿病等長期疾病。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n廣東現尼日利亞變種<br />\n<br />\n此外，廣東省疾控中心上周五首次從兩宗輸入武漢肺炎個案中，發現尼日利亞變種病毒株。有研究指，該變種病毒株令病毒傳播力增強，令曾感染病毒的患者再次感染。<br />\n<br />\n《北京日報》"},{"pid":"f8f1d40252683dce8c4651c396a547e1aa756614","tid":2447150,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T04:15:06.000Z","msg":"777: 香港行先一步<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2633d6f5be2fca03e451a80c3f107fbdb120be12","tid":2447150,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T04:17:31.000Z","msg":"呢d先係愛民政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62a379158cefb349f03824f01567ef7c26c63c8c","tid":2447150,"uid":387826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T04:18:11.000Z","msg":"北京：我知自己嘅疫苗信唔過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6899e8d7253eef946f1141a40dfff6507dc8d0b8","tid":2447150,"uid":393145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T04:23:56.000Z","msg":"林鄭：疫苗好安全 唔打疫苗係自私<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70268c0270407765d8c158b54b640b021d073a21","tid":2447150,"uid":244332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T05:14:30.000Z","msg":"前排有個藍絲，<br />\n話中國俾得香港用一定係最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}